sequenceDiagram
  actor A as User A
  actor B as User B
  participant S as Server
  participant DB as MySQL
  A->>S: POST connect_request A->B
  S->>DB: INSERT PENDING
  S-->>A: Request sent
  B->>S: POST connect_request B->A
  S->>DB: UPDATE both ACCEPTED
  S-->>B: Connected!
  A->>S: POST send_message
  S->>DB: INSERT message
  A->>S: GET fetch_messages
  S->>DB: SELECT thread
  S-->>A: {messages}